EmailTemplate.name: Preschool Directors thank you
EmailTemplate.subject: Twilight Tour 3 April: Thank you for your support
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Contact.FirstName}
<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" />
I just wanted to drop you a note to thank you for supporting our Kindergarten Twilight Tour in your centre. We had an overwhelming response from families and today we have been inundated with calls and equiries for our Kindergarten program.
To thank you for your support, I would like to offer you two complimentary tickets to our production of Beauty and the Beast. Showing at NIDA Parade Theatre from 10 - 12 April, it's a wonderful insight into the wealth of talented student performers that we have here at St Andrew's Cathedral School.
If you would like to come along, just let me know and I can arrange to have your name on the door.
{!Contact.FirstName}, thank you again and I look forward to being in touch regarding our School Readiness Talk in July.
Regards,
Robyn
Robyn Pedley Enrolments Assistant
St Andrew's Cathedral School
